## Summary
This documentation details the Movable Ink integration with Amplitude, which enables marketers to create personalized content based on user behavior data from Amplitude's User Profile API. The integration allows for real-time personalization across customer engagement channels by streaming events and user properties to Movable Ink, with specific setup steps required in both platforms.

